sale and lease-back arrangement, and Rhondda and Mid-Glamorgan local
authorities have agreed to provide bank guarantees worth Pounds 350,000.
The group also has a cost-cutting programme including redundancies, and is
considering mergers or disposals. No improvement in sales is expected until
1993.
